headline: VKTX Finishes Enrolment in Mid-Stage Study on Oral Weight-Loss Drug
summary: Viking enrolls around 280 participants in the phase II study evaluating the oral version of its obesity drug. Data from this study is expected in 2H25.

headline: How AZ and Amgen’s Tezspire respiratory data ups the ‘level of ambition’ in immunology
summary: After Tezspire reduced the need for nasal polyp surgery by 98% in patients with a severe respiratory condition, the biopharma giants are even more ambitious for the next wave of biologic medicines.
